result.name: Wang Jia Sha

reviews.text: The food there is so good and i must go there again
Poor service. Very expensive. A plain bland bowl of noodle for one person costs $100 in total with extra add on costs - noodle + tea fee + peanut fee + service charge. Ridiculous! 😡
Good service, while food items are not cheap, the quality is quite good and not oily . Fried egg yolk filled with red bean paste is wonderful.

I’m surprised to see the really poor ratings for this place. Originally, I never went because the reviews were bad. Decided to give it a shot after they renovated the place. I had the 小籠包，紅油抄手，乾扁四季豆，上海炒麵. The taste was all very good and the price isn’t too bad. For the Tai Koo Area I was pleasantly surprised. If you are comparing to Din Tai Fung or crystal Jade then you will be disappointed. But overall I thought it was a good meal. Especially the 乾扁四季豆。
Good service, above average food

reviews.text:
It is a good place to walk around. You may find different themes in the hall. This time, you see lovely Line Friends here. You can take lots of good photos since different interesting figures here. You can find a large Brown as well as human size figures.
In addition, a lot of variety stores can be found. There is also a brand new theater as well as food courts. 
You can also find ice skating and super market. Anyway, you name it, you can find it.

I have the best experience in here. Concierge is very polite and helpful. You have a lot of choices in terms of restaurants if you are a food lover. Everything you want you can find just in there. Staffs and shops service are very satisfactory. Live simply live happy

You can get pretty much everything here. My only gripe is that periodically they will swap the shop locations around......

Really do like the events they run at the centre stage
A nice place to dining , to shopping , A very good environment centre to spend your good time with your children in here on Saturday and Sunday holidays.
Recommend to go before 1100 on weekends if you drive. Shop $350+ and park free.
